{"tid":149170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人牙骹擘大口會啪一聲","createTime":"2017-03-09T05:50:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T14:43:21.000Z","uid":36341,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0f448e3f850a372c378c47170e9f02dbd74aeab3","tid":149170,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:50:57.000Z","msg":"幾年前覺得一邊牙骹緊咗 好似擘唔盡個口<br />\n忍咗個幾月決定出盡力擘大個口<br />\n結果鬆咗之後每次擘大口果個位都會啪一聲<br />\n啪咗幾年 其實係咪甩咗骹<br />\n雖然唔痛 但我驚啪得多一邊牙骹啲骨會啪大<br />\n有冇巴打分享吓"},{"pid":"77e0069191b3b20cdac816b529f39ba0648154e5","tid":149170,"uid":83496,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:53:21.000Z","msg":"你老母牙骹擘大口都會啪一聲"},{"pid":"1350858021b1d36dddf436c09611589eeb0f71b5","tid":149170,"uid":50952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:54:25.000Z","msg":"岩岩擘大口真係會啪一下<br />\n好多年好似冇點留意"},{"pid":"8ae8cd31a2ed27d610356d8d8fca549cd11581f2","tid":149170,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:54:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老母牙骹擘大口都會啪一聲</blockquote><br />\n你冇撚嘢呀？"},{"pid":"947b7d0040e0b8c5de97c8596e41f1a695e79cbe","tid":149170,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:55:01.000Z","msg":"有時打喊露都會"},{"pid":"14bb280e164ab9fab459435d4e2c91d81b3eae70","tid":149170,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:55:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩擘大口真係會啪一下<br />\n好多年好似冇點留意</blockquote><br />\n係咪得一邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1691a22018126550cdeaf85a85889d92818869e6","tid":149170,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T05:57:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時打喊露都會</blockquote><br />\n但我家陣次次擘大口都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試過有次周圍好靜 有人坐我隔黎 我擘大口啪咗聲<br />\n佢望咗過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d01aeba41b77054fb40a463136a55fb5611fb4","tid":149170,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:02:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7aa7f5dc89f87610ebcac676f67ff25498255d4","tid":149170,"uid":24935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:03:46.000Z","msg":"Cool 牙之前有，cool 完牙之後無左。<br />\n<br />\n點解有聲醫生係cool 牙前同我講話我個牙骹&quot;歪&quot;左<br />\nCool 牙過程會自己正番，而家cool 完之後已經無哂聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c8ccd31a90ef5d9e34cb20170a3c904cce34643","tid":149170,"uid":34209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:05:41.000Z","msg":"我牙醫話經常咬硬野就會咁樣"},{"pid":"200e5dba923a3b234fcd71c0b55524581396e5ce","tid":149170,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:07:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cool 牙之前有，cool 完牙之後無左。<br />\n<br />\n點解有聲醫生係cool 牙前同我講話我個牙骹&quot;歪&quot;左<br />\nCool 牙過程會自己正番，而家cool 完之後已經無哂聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真 我個fd都係咁 <br />\n不過佢個程況俾你差d<br />\n<br />\n1.戴牙膠固定先<br />\n2.然後先再cool牙<br />\n3.最後cool完牙睇情況做唔做手術<br />\n<br />\n建議樓主搵牙醫睇下 我fd係照完x光左右唔對稱 唔知乜撚野過長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e685e7ee476b08ae4a7a4d34b4814b5de9a124","tid":149170,"uid":44243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"我係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />左邊會甩左下咁既聲"},{"pid":"c5cf1f97a986d3180caae431d45001aab9658567","tid":149170,"uid":87591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:09:38.000Z","msg":"我都會情况同你差不多"},{"pid":"5d097d4b441821dd998edb36b880372ee5d1b891","tid":149170,"uid":14862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:10:44.000Z","msg":"我右邊會啪一聲<br />\n有時會冇左聲,但個口同時擘唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63e9551800f1fef8a1194b9f869113a785b2aee0","tid":149170,"uid":89722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:12:29.000Z","msg":"我有時想講野會講唔到出聲 唔知關唔關事 如果唔關我要去睇心理醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9600e37d15e900114858f8f52cc884af1d29b0","tid":149170,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我右邊會啪一聲<br />\n有時會冇左聲,但個口同時擘唔大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係喇係喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0741f6da245af29e2c5756789fba984f08c5f7af","tid":149170,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:14:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我有時想講野會講唔到出聲 唔知關唔關事 如果唔關我要去睇心理醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6bb9740560e3c1ed68b761247f40cf00c99d101","tid":149170,"uid":43523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:20:55.000Z","msg":"識人打喊路打到下巴甩臼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67fa1ce8ccfbee3b0c93cb9b4fad073a6a984f53","tid":149170,"uid":57928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"試過 過咗幾個月自己好返"},{"pid":"5fd08a65caaad01f0e5dddb075b644ba4e1a009a","tid":149170,"uid":42485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:26:25.000Z","msg":"係地鐵一擘開個口成粒香口膠跌左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e488b15999bc239e94ad11c097b0184809305fea","tid":149170,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T06:28:31.000Z","msg":"我兩邊都有聲，已經好多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\